  'e1ca2a4d-34a6-48aa-a6f2-e571dc95e06a', 2025, '6.3', '2025-6.3', 'Choosing a free adventure trip for the school: Australia, Iceland or Morocco',
  'Group Interaction', 'A travel agency''s website',
  '["Once-in-a-lifetime adventures\nHere at Global Travel, we''ve specialised in delivering unforgettable educational tours to places all over the world for over 50 years. Take a look at our current trips on offer.\nSwim with turtles in Australia\nSwim with endangered species at the world-famous Ningaloo Reef, home to around 500 types of fish and other sea creatures. At only 100 metres offshore,there''s no need to scuba dive-the snorkelling is amazing.See the seven species of turtles that build their nests on beaches and islands nearby. You can also learn how to save coral reefs, which play a vital role in the marine environment.\nVisit a volcanic cave in Iceland\nTravel down 120m below the surface of the earth into an ancient volcanic cave. Explore the colourful rock formations and the huge underground spaces. Above ground, visit the ice lakes to see the incredible filming locations of movies like Star Wars and TV shows like Game of Thrones. You''ll be amazed by the views as you learn more about the rocks we take for granted.\nSee the starry night in Morocco\nMorocco, in North Africa, has some of the world''s best skies for stargazing. The dry climate means cloudless skies all year round, with no towns or light pollution in its remote nature reserves. Experience a unique camping tour in the desert with dedicated guides who know all the best places to see these heavenly wonders. Find out about the history of our universe from the very heart of the desert."]'::jsonb,
  '["which trip would be most beneficial for students to join", "problems and challenges that the students might face on the trip", "how to convince parents to let their children join the trip", "anything else you think is important"]'::jsonb,
  '[{"text": "Have you ever been on a school trip?", "number": 1, "difficulty": "medium", "difficulty_level": "4-6"}, {"text": "Would you like to go on an adventure trip?", "number": 2, "difficulty": "medium", "difficulty_level": "4-6"}, {"text": "Would you prefer to take a relaxing trip or an adventure trip?", "number": 3, "difficulty": "medium", "difficulty_level": "4-6"}, {"text": "Do you think adventure trips are appropriate for students?", "number": 4, "difficulty": "medium", "difficulty_level": "4-6"}, {"text": "Would you prefer to travel to far away places or to stay near to Hong Kong?", "number": 5, "difficulty": "medium", "difficulty_level": "4-6"}, {"text": "Would you prefer going on a trip with your school or with your family?", "number": 6, "difficulty": "medium", "difficulty_level": "4-6"}, {"text": "Are you interested in exploring marine life?", "number": 7, "difficulty": "medium", "difficulty_level": "4-6"}, {"text": "What makes an adventure trip memorable?", "number": 8, "difficulty": "medium", "difficulty_level": "4-6"}]'::jsonb,
